OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThames Water makes bid to  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Flift bills by up to 44%    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Thames Water is attempting to persuade 
OL,6, the regulator to let it raise consumer 
OL,7, bills by up to 44% over the next five  
OL,8, years by increasing investment.        
OL,10,FThe heavily indebted water firm aims to
OL,11,Fspend at least #1.1bn more on          
OL,12,Fenvironmental measures.                
OL,14,FRegulator Ofwat had dismissed the      
OL,15,Fcompany's original proposal, leading to
OL,16,Fquestions over the firm's future.      
OL,18,FThames's huge debts have led to        
OL,19,Fspeculation it could be taken over by  
OL,20,Fthe government.                        
